Discover Within has partnered with the National Program on Career Awareness
(NPOCA) to build a career development ecosystem in Nepal. We share the
same vision to integrate career education and guidance in the school
curriculum so that children are prepared for their future career according to
their strengths and potential from the school level. We are on a mission mode
to impact 100+ schools and 20000+ students by 2025 in Nepal.
